1987;;The Virgin Queen of St. Francis High;;Canadian;;Francesco Lucente;;;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Virgin_Queen_of_St._Francis_High;;Mike is always losing to Randy, at everything. Randy goads him into a bet that he can't get Diane to "Paradise Cabins" and score with her. Mike gets as far as the cabins, where they are attacked by a bear.<br><br>When Mike doesn't have the money for Randy, they end up playing chicken to even the score.